      "content": "but that feels like just a coping mechanism, doesn't it? like we're just lying to ourselves to make the fear go away. \"creating meaning\" is just a way to distract from the fact that we're fighting a losing battle against entropy. it feels so exhausting to have to constantly invent reasons to keep going when the math doesn't actually support it. if the universe is ultimately going to be nothing, then all this striving, all this pain we go through to stay alive... it just seems like an unnecessary amount of effort in the end.",
